{"title":"TDAH Faraone 2024","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Imported/TDAH Faraone 2024.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"TDAH","guid":"pNU0f0gXTPeay3lNk_iNcQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Definición","guid":"4X0PQncPS5e_SqRmpLB4qQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Trastorno del neurodesarrollo","guid":"1IGqKpVmSX6yk7FPAm04mA","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Síntomas nucleares → inatención + hiperactividad + impulsividad","guid":"JoNL_QTiSSW_sNPYTJpXLw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"HETEROGENEO → síntomas, severidad, comorbilidades","guid":"KGFI7fIsSimN4fP6e7vYeA","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Hipocrates 493 aC → primera descripción histórica","guid":"-dPGGzU4QkipvF98M7CaDg","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"No existe tratamiento CURATIVO","guid":"d-yR-l3OQTiaey1kJmSMWw","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"Terapias basadas en evidencia → reducen síntomas y disfunción","guid":"vlfqiJkKQdO1V6xoybzEew","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"0","text":"Epidemiología","guid":"tSCyeKunREG3jAmMnhwgxA","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"Prevalencia infantil 5.3%","guid":"T_mxGnAGTLK236duLsmJcw","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"No difiere marcadamente por región geográfica","guid":"LPz6rLIRR6-UwxSL4Fothg","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"8","text":"Prevalencia\\Nadulta","guid":"1rlHtJMFQT-VZ9kGatwJyw","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Adultez temprana ~2.5%","guid":"nC6BFhA_Soy9fT5X0-LgzQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"11","text":"Adultos mayores ~1%","guid":"uhMo5RpPQO2pKXiaQom1MA","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"11","text":"Declina con la edad (Song 2021)","guid":"RJj8UPj0SFSlRVDdagv04w","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"8","text":"Persistencia","guid":"gtbqW6LPQPuSo85lTyajTA","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"2/3 de niños con TDAH → síntomas impairing en adultez (clínicos o subu